T*
(source?) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Study Tips After Reading) Tj
T*
(- Rewrite the overview of Nutrition in your own words after studying it.) Tj
T*
(- Use short exercises built around diet and nutrient-function questions before trying) Tj
T*
(harder tasks.) Tj
T*
(- Keep track of mistakes such as calling every food nutrient an energy source and write) Tj
T*
(the correction beside each one.) Tj
T*
(- Revise Nutrition regularly so the method behind balanced diet, nutrients, and food) Tj
T*
(functions becomes familiar.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Independent Practice) Tj
T*
